          <div class="pricing-card__note">Hall sensor · Drain pump · Thermal fuse · Vent cleaning</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="pricing-card__appliance">Dishwasher / Oven</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__range">$150 – $450</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__note">Miele error codes · Gas igniter · Scale · Calibration</div>
        </div>
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <div class="pricing-card__appliance">Diagnostic Fee</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__range">$89</div>
          <div class="pricing-card__note">Waived when you proceed with the repair</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="wv-faq">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Questions Westlake Village Customers Ask</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you offer same-day appliance repair in Westlake Village, CA?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Our Thousand Oaks branch covers all of Westlake Village — Westlake Lake, Lake Sherwood, North Ranch, Westlake Trails, and all of 91361 and 91362. Call before noon for same-day afternoon service.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Does the Las Virgenes water in Westlake Village affect appliances?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. LVMWD delivers 200–250 mg/L hardness throughout Westlake Village. Ice maker inlet valves and dishwasher spray arms accumulate mineral deposits faster here. We test for this proactively on every relevant call.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you repair Sub-Zero, Wolf, Thermador, and Miele appliances in Westlake Village?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Sub-Zero, Wolf, Thermador, Miele, and Viking are standard throughout Westlake Village's lake and estate homes. We carry OEM parts for these brands on every vehicle.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Can you service appliances in Westlake Village's gated communities?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. We coordinate gate access in advance for Westlake Village's gated communities and work with estate managers and property managers as needed.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Are you available on weekends in Westlake Village?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Saturday 8am–7pm and Sunday 9am–5pm.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">What is your diagnostic fee in Westlake Village?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Our diagnostic fee is $89, waived when you proceed with the repair. Written estimate before we start. Most Westlake Village repairs run $150–$500.</div></details>
        <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">Do you also serve Thousand Oaks, Calabasas, and Agoura Hills?</summary><div class="faq-answer">Yes. Our Westlake Village service extends to Thousand Oaks, Calabasas, Agoura Hills, Oak Park, Newbury Park, and all of the Conejo Valley.</div></details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

